In http://www.tuhs.org/Archive/PDP-11/Tools/Tapes/
there are tools that I and other wrote to create
tape images: tp etc.

So you could do:

	tar vxf 1bsd.tar
	tp tool to build a tp image
	mktap to build a SimH tap image
	attach to SimH
	PROFIT!!

So sorry, I couldn't stop myself.

Cheers, Warren

